  invoiceId: 
}

docs {
  ### Export Client Invoice PDF
  Generates and downloads a real TAX-INVOICE PDF for the specified Client Invoice ID.
  
  **Note**: Access is restricted to Clients, Client Users, and assigned Transporters.
}
